[{"text": "Words matter.", "start": 13.96, "duration": 2.28}, {"text": "They can heal", "start": 19.48, "duration": 2.176}, {"text": "and they can kill ...", "start": 21.68, "duration": 1.28}, {"text": "yet, they have a limit.", "start": 24.04, "duration": 2.92}, {"text": "When I was in eighth grade,", "start": 28.96, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "my teacher gave me a vocabulary sheet", "start": 32.6, "duration": 4.016}, {"text": "with the word \"genocide.\"", "start": 36.64, "duration": 2.56}, {"text": "I hated it.", "start": 43.12, "duration": 2.64}, {"text": "The word genocide is clinical ...", "start": 46.84, "duration": 4.48}, {"text": "overgeneral ...", "start": 52.48, "duration": 1.52}, {"text": "bloodless ...", "start": 56.64, "duration": 2.136}, {"text": "dehumanizing.", "start": 58.8, "duration": 1.84}, {"text": "No word", "start": 63.28, "duration": 1.52}, {"text": "can describe", "start": 66.24, "duration": 2.176}, {"text": "what this does to a nation.", "start": 68.44, "duration": 3.12}, {"text": "You need to know,", "start": 74.16, "duration": 1.736}, {"text": "in this kind of war,", "start": 75.92, "duration": 1.68}, {"text": "husbands kills wives,", "start": 79.12, "duration": 2.48}, {"text": "wives kill husbands,", "start": 82.64, "duration": 2.44}, {"text": "neighbors and friends kill each other.", "start": 86.6, "duration": 3.36}, {"text": "Someone", "start": 93.64, "duration": 1.32}, {"text": "in power", "start": 96.12, "duration": 1.216}, {"text": "says,", "start": 97.36, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "\"Those over there ...", "start": 99.96, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "they don't belong.", "start": 102.52, "duration": 1.28}, {"text": "They're not human.\"", "start": 104.68, "duration": 1.36}, {"text": "And people believe it.", "start": 107.12, "duration": 2.24}, {"text": "I don't want words", "start": 111.76, "duration": 2.336}, {"text": "to describe this kind of behavior.", "start": 114.12, "duration": 2.52}, {"text": "I want words to stop it.", "start": 118.72, "duration": 3.6}, {"text": "But where are the words to stop this?", "start": 124.8, "duration": 2.68}, {"text": "And how do we find the words?", "start": 128.12, "duration": 3.28}, {"text": "But I believe, truly,\nwe have to keep trying.", "start": 134.12, "duration": 5.64}, {"text": "I was born in Kigali, Rwanda.", "start": 141.96, "duration": 2.64}, {"text": "I felt loved by my entire family", "start": 146.12, "duration": 4.12}, {"text": "and my neighbors.", "start": 151.24, "duration": 1.36}, {"text": "I was constantly\nbeing teased by everybody,", "start": 154.0, "duration": 4.296}, {"text": "especially my two older siblings.", "start": 158.32, "duration": 2.6}, {"text": "When I lost my front tooth,", "start": 162.24, "duration": 1.96}, {"text": "my brother looked at me and said,", "start": 165.44, "duration": 2.096}, {"text": "\"Oh, it has happened to you, too?", "start": 167.56, "duration": 2.6}, {"text": "It will never grow back.\"", "start": 171.92, "duration": 1.496}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 173.44, "duration": 1.016}, {"text": "I enjoyed playing everywhere,", "start": 174.48, "duration": 2.216}, {"text": "especially my mother's garden\nand my neighbor's.", "start": 176.72, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "I loved my kindergarten.", "start": 181.48, "duration": 2.08}, {"text": "We sang songs,", "start": 184.44, "duration": 2.416}, {"text": "we played everywhere", "start": 186.88, "duration": 1.256}, {"text": "and ate lunch.", "start": 188.16, "duration": 1.48}, {"text": "I had a childhood", "start": 191.6, "duration": 3.336}, {"text": "that I would wish for anyone.", "start": 194.96, "duration": 3.72}, {"text": "But when I was six,", "start": 200.68, "duration": 1.72}, {"text": "the adults in my family\nbegan to speak in whispers", "start": 203.4, "duration": 5.616}, {"text": "and shushed me any time\nthat I asked a question.", "start": 209.04, "duration": 3.84}, {"text": "One night,", "start": 215.0, "duration": 1.256}, {"text": "my mom and dad came.", "start": 216.28, "duration": 1.68}, {"text": "They had this strange look\nwhen they woke us.", "start": 219.2, "duration": 2.72}, {"text": "They sent my older sister Claire and I\nto our grandparent's,", "start": 223.64, "duration": 5.296}, {"text": "hoping whatever was happening\nwould blow away.", "start": 228.96, "duration": 2.92}, {"text": "Soon we had to escape from there, too.", "start": 234.16, "duration": 3.52}, {"text": "We hid,", "start": 239.4, "duration": 1.416}, {"text": "we crawled,", "start": 240.84, "duration": 1.216}, {"text": "we sometimes ran.", "start": 242.08, "duration": 1.28}, {"text": "Sometimes I heard laughter", "start": 248.84, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "and then screaming and crying", "start": 254.88, "duration": 3.52}, {"text": "and then noise that I had never heard.", "start": 259.6, "duration": 2.52}, {"text": "You see,", "start": 264.0, "duration": 1.216}, {"text": "I did not know", "start": 265.24, "duration": 1.88}, {"text": "what those noises were.", "start": 269.04, "duration": 2.64}, {"text": "They were neither human --", "start": 272.56, "duration": 2.296}, {"text": "and also at the same time,\nthey were human.", "start": 274.88, "duration": 2.48}, {"text": "I saw people who were not breathing.", "start": 278.68, "duration": 3.8}, {"text": "I thought they were asleep.", "start": 283.92, "duration": 1.84}, {"text": "I still didn't understand what death was,", "start": 288.48, "duration": 4.896}, {"text": "or killing in itself.", "start": 293.4, "duration": 2.52}, {"text": "When we would stop\nto rest for a little bit", "start": 297.76, "duration": 3.496}, {"text": "or search for food,", "start": 301.28, "duration": 1.936}, {"text": "I would close my eyes,", "start": 303.24, "duration": 1.936}, {"text": "hoping when I opened them,", "start": 305.2, "duration": 2.536}, {"text": "I would be awake.", "start": 307.76, "duration": 1.4}, {"text": "I had no idea which direction was home.", "start": 311.48, "duration": 3.36}, {"text": "Days were for hiding", "start": 316.8, "duration": 1.96}, {"text": "and night for walking.", "start": 320.12, "duration": 1.92}, {"text": "You go from a person who's away from home", "start": 328.28, "duration": 5.016}, {"text": "to a person with no home.", "start": 333.32, "duration": 2.24}, {"text": "The place that is supposed to want you", "start": 337.2, "duration": 2.656}, {"text": "has pushed you out,", "start": 339.88, "duration": 1.68}, {"text": "and no one takes you in.", "start": 344.36, "duration": 3.56}, {"text": "You are unwanted", "start": 348.76, "duration": 2.36}, {"text": "by anyone.", "start": 352.16, "duration": 2.44}, {"text": "You are a refugee.", "start": 356.76, "duration": 2.32}, {"text": "From age six to 12,", "start": 362.24, "duration": 2.216}, {"text": "I lived in seven different countries,", "start": 364.48, "duration": 2.28}, {"text": "moving from one refugee camp to another,", "start": 368.56, "duration": 3.2}, {"text": "hoping we would be wanted.", "start": 372.72, "duration": 2.44}, {"text": "My older sister Claire,", "start": 378.2, "duration": 2.376}, {"text": "she became a young mother ...", "start": 380.6, "duration": 1.88}, {"text": "and a master at getting things done.", "start": 385.32, "duration": 3.12}, {"text": "When I was 12,", "start": 389.92, "duration": 1.896}, {"text": "I came to America with Claire\nand her family on refugee status.", "start": 391.84, "duration": 4.72}, {"text": "And that's only the beginning,", "start": 399.96, "duration": 2.656}, {"text": "because even though I was 12 years old,", "start": 402.64, "duration": 3.016}, {"text": "sometimes I felt like three years old", "start": 405.68, "duration": 2.216}, {"text": "and sometimes 50 years old.", "start": 407.92, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "My past receded,", "start": 410.96, "duration": 1.816}, {"text": "grew jumbled,", "start": 412.8, "duration": 1.216}, {"text": "distorted.", "start": 414.04, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "Everything was too much", "start": 416.2, "duration": 2.856}, {"text": "and nothing.", "start": 419.08, "duration": 1.36}, {"text": "Time seemed like pages torn out of a book", "start": 422.88, "duration": 5.136}, {"text": "and scattered everywhere.", "start": 428.04, "duration": 1.88}, {"text": "This still happens to me\nstanding right here.", "start": 431.6, "duration": 4.8}, {"text": "After I got to America,", "start": 440.8, "duration": 2.08}, {"text": "Claire and I did not talk about our past.", "start": 445.84, "duration": 3.04}, {"text": "In 2006,", "start": 451.4, "duration": 2.216}, {"text": "after 12 years", "start": 453.64, "duration": 1.68}, {"text": "being separated away from my family,", "start": 457.44, "duration": 1.896}, {"text": "and then seven years\nknowing that they were dead", "start": 459.36, "duration": 2.776}, {"text": "and them thinking that we were dead,", "start": 462.16, "duration": 1.84}, {"text": "we reunited ...", "start": 464.88, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "in the most dramatic,\nAmerican way possible.", "start": 467.48, "duration": 5.48}, {"text": "Live,", "start": 473.88, "duration": 1.896}, {"text": "on television --", "start": 475.8, "duration": 1.616}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 477.44, "duration": 1.136}, {"text": "on \"The Oprah Show.\"", "start": 478.6, "duration": 1.416}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 480.04, "duration": 1.816}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 481.88, "duration": 4.4}, {"text": "I told you, I told you.", "start": 489.0, "duration": 1.936}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 490.96, "duration": 1.32}, {"text": "But after the show,", "start": 493.84, "duration": 1.84}, {"text": "as I spent time with my mom and dad", "start": 500.84, "duration": 4.976}, {"text": "and my little sister", "start": 505.84, "duration": 2.656}, {"text": "and my two new siblings that I never met,", "start": 508.52, "duration": 2.88}, {"text": "I felt anger.", "start": 513.2, "duration": 2.16}, {"text": "I felt every deep pain in me.", "start": 516.96, "duration": 4.2}, {"text": "And I know that\nthere is absolutely nothing,", "start": 523.52, "duration": 4.896}, {"text": "nothing,", "start": 528.44, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "that could restore the time\nwe lost with each other", "start": 530.44, "duration": 5.056}, {"text": "and the relationship we could've had.", "start": 535.52, "duration": 2.72}, {"text": "Soon, my parents\nmoved to the United States,", "start": 540.48, "duration": 4.176}, {"text": "but like Claire,", "start": 544.68, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "they don't talk about our past.", "start": 547.2, "duration": 3.52}, {"text": "They live in never-ending present.", "start": 552.2, "duration": 4.016}, {"text": "Not asking too many questions,", "start": 556.24, "duration": 3.016}, {"text": "not allowing themselves to feel --", "start": 559.28, "duration": 3.44}, {"text": "moving in small steps.", "start": 564.24, "duration": 3.64}, {"text": "None of us, of course,\ncan make sense of what happened to us.", "start": 569.8, "duration": 4.96}, {"text": "Though my family is alive --", "start": 578.68, "duration": 2.72}, {"text": "yes, we were broken,", "start": 582.84, "duration": 2.576}, {"text": "and yes, we are numb", "start": 585.44, "duration": 2.736}, {"text": "and we were silenced\nby our own experience.", "start": 588.2, "duration": 4.8}, {"text": "It's not just my family.", "start": 595.8, "duration": 4.52}, {"text": "Rwanda is not the only country", "start": 602.32, "duration": 4.776}, {"text": "where people have turned on each other", "start": 607.12, "duration": 2.936}, {"text": "and murdered each other.", "start": 610.08, "duration": 1.44}, {"text": "The entire human race,", "start": 613.44, "duration": 2.36}, {"text": "in many ways,", "start": 617.64, "duration": 1.256}, {"text": "is like my family.", "start": 618.92, "duration": 1.52}, {"text": "Not dead;", "start": 623.8, "duration": 1.696}, {"text": "yes, broken, numb and silenced\nby the violence of the world", "start": 625.52, "duration": 6.056}, {"text": "that has taken over.", "start": 631.6, "duration": 1.68}, {"text": "You see,", "start": 635.68, "duration": 1.216}, {"text": "the chaos of the violence continues inside", "start": 636.92, "duration": 4.936}, {"text": "in the words we use", "start": 641.88, "duration": 3.136}, {"text": "and the stories\nwe create every single day.", "start": 645.04, "duration": 4.08}, {"text": "But also on the labels\nthat we impose on ourselves", "start": 651.48, "duration": 5.616}, {"text": "and each other.", "start": 657.12, "duration": 1.36}, {"text": "Once we call someone \"other,\"", "start": 661.32, "duration": 5.096}, {"text": "\"less than,\"", "start": 666.44, "duration": 1.336}, {"text": "\"one of them\"", "start": 667.8, "duration": 1.256}, {"text": "or \"better than,\"", "start": 669.08, "duration": 1.36}, {"text": "believe me ...", "start": 671.6, "duration": 1.24}, {"text": "under the right condition,", "start": 676.08, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "it's a short path to more destruction.", "start": 680.16, "duration": 4.4}, {"text": "More chaos", "start": 685.88, "duration": 1.816}, {"text": "and more noise", "start": 687.72, "duration": 1.336}, {"text": "that we will not understand.", "start": 689.08, "duration": 2.2}, {"text": "Words will never be enough", "start": 693.08, "duration": 3.04}, {"text": "to quantify and qualify\nthe many magnitudes", "start": 697.48, "duration": 5.336}, {"text": "of human-caused destruction.", "start": 702.84, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "In order for us", "start": 709.52, "duration": 2.32}, {"text": "to stop the violence\nthat goes on in the world,", "start": 713.04, "duration": 4.2}, {"text": "I hope --", "start": 719.6, "duration": 1.736}, {"text": "at least I beg you --", "start": 721.36, "duration": 2.536}, {"text": "to pause.", "start": 723.92, "duration": 1.28}, {"text": "Let's ask ourselves:", "start": 726.96, "duration": 2.04}, {"text": "Who are we without words?", "start": 731.0, "duration": 3.4}, {"text": "Who are we without labels?", "start": 736.08, "duration": 3.68}, {"text": "Who are we in our breath?", "start": 741.48, "duration": 3.24}, {"text": "Who are we in our heartbeat?", "start": 746.64, "duration": 4.8}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 753.0, "duration": 4.76}]